reviewText: Great show! I have visited the hanger and they are very nice people.  The show itself is entertaining and fun to watch.

So often 5 years of a reality series tends to make it, "long in the tooth."  Not so Season Five of Ice Pilots.  Flying 70 year old planes in well below zero weather conditions means anything can happen.  I have found each epidsoe of this season very interesting.
Great series! I can't wait for the sixth season to come out.
I really enjoy watching the DVDs.
One of a kind! Can't stop watching it.
Well worth watching for aviation enthusiasts.
Finally I have the last in the series.  These are not cheap, but to me, they are well worth the money.
Have loved the previous 4 seasons and season 5 has been just as good. Am looking forward to season 6 but sad that this will be the last.
